   ASHLAND OIL Inc. (Ashland, Ky.) -- G. Thomas Wilkinson was
named president of Ashland Exploration Inc., the company's
oil and gas production unit, and a vice president of the
parent company. Mr. Wilkinson, formerly executive vice
president of Ashland Exploration, succeeds James R. Boyd, who
continues as a senior vice president and group operating
officer of Ashland Oil. Ashland is mainly a refiner and
