<LP>
   ST. LOUIS -- Comprehensive Care Corp. said its newly
elected board named James P. Carmany, 51 years old, as
president and chief executive officer.
   Mr. Carmany, a former executive vice president who left
the company last year in a dispute with management, also was
named a director.
</LP>
